name: Looking For A Way
description:
When failure comes for the first time, we are never ready to face it. Feelings of sadness and frustration overwhelm this body.

By the time I woke up, I had fallen very deep. surrounded by darkness and silence. Like a nightmare, but it's not.

It took a long time to get up. Strengthen body and soul. Get ready to step back looking for a way to get out of this darkness.
~"Failure is not the end of everything"~
